import React, { useState } from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Container,
  Typography,
  Grid,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  CardHeader,
  List,
  ListItem,
  ListItemText,
  ListItemIcon,
  Divider,
  Button,
  Avatar,
  Chip,
  LinearProgress,
} from '@mui/material';
import {
  Person,
  ShoppingCart,
  LocalShipping,
  Star,
  TrendingUp,
  Notifications,
  Message,
} from '@mui/icons-material';

const DashboardPage = () => {
  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState('overview');

  const recentActivities = [
    { id: 1, type: 'order', message: 'New order received for Rice Husk', time: '2 hours ago' },
    { id: 2, type: 'message', message: 'New message from Punjab Agro Farms', time: '3 hours ago' },
    { id: 3, type: 'review', message: 'New review received for your product', time: '5 hours ago' },
  ];

  const stats = {
    totalProducts: 12,
    activeListings: 8,
    totalOrders: 45,
    totalRevenue: 125000,
    averageRating: 4.5,
  };

  return (
    <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ mt: 4, mb: 4 }}>
      <Grid container spacing={3}>
        {/* Profile Section */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={4}>
          <Card>
            <CardContent>
              <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
                <Avatar sx={{ width: 100, height: 100, mb: 2 }} />
                <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom>
                  John Doe
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  Verified Seller
                </Typography>
                <Chip
                  icon={<Star />}
                  label={`${stats.averageRating} Rating`}
                  color="primary"
                  sx={{ mt: 1 }}
                />
              </Box>
              <Divider sx={{ my: 2 }} />
              <List>
                <ListItem>
                  <ListItemIcon>
                    <ShoppingCart />
                  </ListItemIcon>
                  <ListItemText
                    primary="Total Products"
                    secondary={stats.totalProducts}
                  />
                </ListItem>
                <ListItem>
                  <ListItemIcon>
                    <TrendingUp />
                  </ListItemIcon>
                  <ListItemText
                    primary="Active Listings"
                    secondary={stats.activeListings}
                  />
                </ListItem>
                <ListItem>
                  <ListItemIcon>
                    <LocalShipping />
                  </ListItemIcon>
                  <ListItemText
                    primary="Total Orders"
                    secondary={stats.totalOrders}
                  />
                </ListItem>
              </List>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>

        {/* Main Content */}
        <Grid item xs={12} md={8}>
          <Card>
            <CardHeader
              title="Dashboard Overview"
              action={
                <Button variant="contained" color="primary">
                  Add New Product
                </Button>
              }
            />
            <CardContent>
              <Box sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                  Recent Activities
                </Typography>
                <List>
                  {recentActivities.map((activity) => (
                    <React.Fragment key={activity.id}>
                      <ListItem>
                        <ListItemIcon>
                          {activity.type === 'order' && <ShoppingCart />}
                          {activity.type === 'message' && <Message />}
                          {activity.type === 'review' && <Star />}
                        </ListItemIcon>
                        <ListItemText
                          primary={activity.message}
                          secondary={activity.time}
                        />
                      </ListItem>
                      <Divider />
                    </React.Fragment>
                  ))}
                </List>
              </Box>

              <Box sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                  Sales Performance
                </Typography>
                <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', mb: 1 }}>
                  <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ flex: 1 }}>
                    Monthly Revenue
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                    â‚¹{stats.totalRevenue.toLocaleString()}
                  </Typography>
                </Box>
                <LinearProgress variant="determinate" value={75} sx={{ height: 10, borderRadius: 5 }} />
              </Box>

              <Box>
                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                  Notifications
                </Typography>
                <List>
                  <ListItem>
                    <ListItemIcon>
                      <Notifications />
                    </ListItemIcon>
                    <ListItemText
                      primary="System Update Available"
                      secondary="Update your profile information"
                    />
                  </ListItem>
                  <Divider />
                  <ListItem>
                    <ListItemIcon>
                      <Message />
                    </ListItemIcon>
                    <ListItemText
                      primary="New Message"
                      secondary="You have 3 unread messages"
                    />
                  </ListItem>
                </List>
              </Box>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default DashboardPage;
